        <p><strong>Key Achievements:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Signal Path Logic:</strong> Engineered a nine-stage character mapping algorithm (Plugboard \u2192 Rotors \u2192 Reflector \u2192 Rotors \u2192 Plugboard).</li>
                <li><strong>Bug Resolution:</strong> Solved complex plugboard backtracking issues to ensure 100% accuracy in bidirectional character encryption and decryption.</li>
                <li><strong>UI Evolution:</strong> Migrated the project from a CLI-based tool to a custom Java Swing GUI to visualize rotor states and character transformations.</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
